snippet.title: Sky Warriors!
snippet.description:
Hello Pilots!

Sky Warriors is going into soft launch and the game is now available in some lucky countries!!

Please follow us on our social media and share your feedback with us so we can improve even further!
https://linktr.ee/PlaySkyWarriors
